A, B, C, D, E, F, G… Classic Wooden Alphabet Puzzle is designed as an educational tool which encourages children to learn the alphabets and take their first step towards spelling, reading and writing. With no sharp edges, these multi-colored alphabet letters are easy for little hands to hold. Designed for maximum child safety, this puzzle is made of non-toxic water based paints which are 100% child safe. The sturdy design of this puzzle makes it a toy for life. Classic Wooden Alphabet Puzzle is great for enriching a toddler’s cognitive skills, fine motor skills & visual perception skills.
Awesome gift for a preschooler. They will really love playing with this puzzle.

How cute is our little Elephant Wooden Teether! This elephant shaped beech wood teether is expertly designed so that your baby can easily wrap their tiny fingers around it. Your child may have sore or tender gums when their teeth begin to erupt. This teether is the best to soothe those aching gums as well as to entertain your little ones. It also helps to stimulate baby’s sense of feel & touch and to develop hand-eye coordination as your baby learn to bring the teether to their mouth. The Beech wood used for creating this teether is natural and non-toxic, so you can rest assured knowing that its super safe for your little one and their tender gums.
Bring home this TinyBee teether and watch your child indulge in it playfully.

Vroom! Vroom! Make way for TinyBee’s Classic Sports Car which makes your child’s world full of imagination and creative play!
This fascinating miniature vehicle features bright colors, attractive patterns and whimsical designs to make your child wonder and spark their imagination. This wheeling fun toy is a perfect playmate for your child to race around the house, create stories and pretend play. This easy to grip vehicle will hone your child’s cognitive skills, gross motor skills and spatial awareness. Designed for maximum child safety, this toy is made of natural wood & non-toxic water-based paints which are 100% child safe. The sturdy design of this toy makes it durable enough to keep rolling for generations of play.
A wonderful addition to your little ones toy collection! Kids will have a rocking good time with this adorable push along miniature vehicle.
